data.description: Located in the historic West End neighborhood of Cambridge, just one block from the Mighty Choptank River. Close to marina, parks, and downtown area. Kitchen features include granite counters, an Island, stainless appliances, and large pantry.  The first floor offers a full bath, living room, and family room. 2nd floor consists of three bedrooms and a full bath, add your finishing touches to the climate-controlled 270sqft bonus room on the 3rd floor. A fully fenced rear yard offers plenty of additional parking or a space to enjoy any time of year with the additional storage shed.
